name: GE90 ENGINE ROAR! Air Canada 777-300ER GORGEOUS Evening Takeoff from Toronto Pearson [4K]
description:
The Boeing 777-300ER is powered by two General Electric GE90-115Bs, the most powerful jet engine in the world, and quite possibly the most distinctive-sounding!

A few weeks ago I rode on this Air Canada 77W out of Toronto and managed to experience this incredible takeoff sound. Trip report on this coming soon!
